{"tid":1965364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本出名帆布袋賣500兩個？ 隨時俾人拎個人資料再呃郵費","createTime":"2020-04-09T12:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T10:53:25.000Z","uid":350743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"334958a4a4cb71e87af687b866fae6a1eacf56dd","tid":1965364,"uid":350743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"近排碌連登見到有個網賣日本帆布袋，click 左入去發現唔多妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nUrl:<a href=\"https://zfb.peafoo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzfb.peafoo.com%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=7c839f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zfb.peafoo.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://liyatoday.com/index/detail.html?sno=ODk1MzEyOTA1&amp;coll_id=999947145&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliyatoday.com%2Findex%2Fdetail.html%3Fsno%3DODk1MzEyOTA1%26coll_id%3D999947145%26&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=e0cd1d4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liyatoday.com/index/detail.html?sno=ODk1MzEyOTA1&amp;coll_id=999947145&amp;</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.成浸支那淘寶柒味 網站冇主頁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/190707_e2e5f0bece3b57cba5055f6c903aa70e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F190707_e2e5f0bece3b57cba5055f6c903aa70e.JPG&h=0785cd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/190747_25e1c0076b0603247efca45403087a3c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F190747_25e1c0076b0603247efca45403087a3c.JPG&h=5c02fd0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾我揾到個有主頁嘅，UI一撚樣，照抄咁款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/191149_9a21e9be1b97119e0debd9990061ea96.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F191149_9a21e9be1b97119e0debd9990061ea96.JPG&h=2ef58f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後主頁賣嘅嘢全部低過半價，會唔會咁大隻夾乸隨街跳？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/191453_8c10940bf50a2a86d50b0d140aa1a7bc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F191453_8c10940bf50a2a86d50b0d140aa1a7bc.JPG&h=9cf989ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/191510_98397719ab3dca0949c2e027eed67696.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F191510_98397719ab3dca0949c2e027eed67696.JPG&h=6b5d7346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.淨係得貨到付款<br />\n<br />\n望落好似好安全，好過比信用卡，但係佢可以用你地址、電話、名，寄垃圾比你然後收你郵費<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ApjgbnrqrZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FApjgbnrqrZY&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=67a48af5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ApjgbnrqrZY</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣好多呢類型嘅詐騙，通常都係呃啲冇乜網絡安全意識嘅人<br />\n<br />\n3.好多幾乎一樣嘅網址<br />\n上面就係我搵到嘅孿生兄弟，做左啲Research之後，發現係中国公司專用黎做詐騙<br />\n<br />\n呢個係上面其中一個網嘅data:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CS4c2xJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCS4c2xJ.jpg&h=9d1f2de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/193119_fea95efa4ef8ac54aadacfcf2d240a77.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F193119_fea95efa4ef8ac54aadacfcf2d240a77.JPG&h=e719be35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Xin Net Technology Corporation</span></span><br />\n<br />\n個網注冊左得個一個月都冇，真係有保證？<br />\n<br />\n呢間垃圾中国公司會copy人地嘅網址，而且十有八九嘅網址都係整呢啲網頁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TanNRzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTanNRzy.jpg&h=9652ebff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gaA39ma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgaA39ma.jpg&h=500e2b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUrl:<a href=\"https://www.prestashop.com/forums/topic/46460-solvedsite-copied-and-hacked-by-chinese-company/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prestashop.com%2Fforums%2Ftopic%2F46460-solvedsite-copied-and-hacked-by-chinese-company%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=3160b8fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.prestashop.com/forums/topic/46460-solvedsite-copied-and-hacked-by-chinese-company/</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣有人整合左呢類嘅詐騙網站特徵<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog-whoscall-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/blog.whoscall.com/2017/08/18/%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E6%8F%AA%E8%A9%90%E9%A8%99%EF%BC%9A-%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%B5%E6%8F%AA%E5%87%BA%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E8%B3%BC%E7%89%A9%E8%A9%90%E9%A8%99/amp/?amp_js_v=a3&amp;amp_gsa=1&amp;usqp=mq331AQFKAGwASA%3D#aoh=15864256071130&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9A%251%24s&amp;ampshare=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.whoscall.com%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%258F%25AA%25E8%25A9%2590%25E9%25A8%2599%25EF%25BC%259A-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E6%258F%25AA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25A9%2590%25E9%25A8%2599%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-whoscall-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fv%2Fs%2Fblog.whoscall.com%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%258F%25AA%25E8%25A9%2590%25E9%25A8%2599%25EF%25BC%259A-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E6%258F%25AA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25A9%2590%25E9%25A8%2599%2Famp%2F%3Famp_js_v%3Da3%26amp_gsa%3D1%2